          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1650385868709-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 16-18 min, turning once halfway, or until everything is cooked through and slightly charred (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>chicken & lamb mixed grill kebabs</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) in a bowl with a small splash of<strong> cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1650385872944-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
