            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>When everything is almost ready, add your <strong>wholemeal pitta[s]</strong> to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until golden and crisp</p><p>Once done, chop the <strong>toasted pittas</strong> in half</p><p>Top the <strong>hummus</strong> with the <strong>crispy lamb </strong>– this is your <strong>crispy lamb hummus</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
