      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken & lamb</strong> <strong>mixed grill kebabs</strong> with the <strong>tomato salad</strong>, <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>pitta halves</strong> and the <strong>crispy lamb hummus</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>garlic sauce</strong> over the kebabs</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
